Cloud Computing. It is the process of abstraction in
that a virtual machine comprising of storage,
processing power and computing resances is created over on
actual physical machine. Thus, Virtualization can be viewed
humerous logical machines made out of a physical
This virtualization is carried out by a software known as
Hypervisor or Virtual Machine Monitor (UMM) which allocates
or distributes resources to make a number of Urstual machines
